body:
### expected behaviour
i can't save the ladp config. after leaveing the administrator site the content should not be changed automaticly from the system (white background for right configuraiton).

### actual behaviour

after i leave the administrator site the content from the field basis-bn and password goes wrong (yellow backgroud) but the content is still the same. so the problem is after leaving the admin site no ldap user can login. if i leave the admin site open everything is ok and the users can login.

